      <abstract obkms_id="6a663874-57be-45f8-9eac-e3b40b350bf4" obkms_process="TRUE">
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>A new combination, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="e3522519-4a92-4845-806f-a9ddfd99e520" obkms_process="TRUE">Lapanthus vidaliorum</tp:taxon-name></italic> (O.B.C. Ribeiro &amp; C.C. Paula) Louzada &amp; Wand. is proposed for <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="f8d9cc6d-f4de-46ae-9d38-bd0f595196d7" obkms_process="TRUE">Orthophytum vidaliorum</tp:taxon-name></italic> O.B.C. Ribeiro &amp; C.C. Paula. In addition notes on taxonomy, geographic distribution and conservation are provided.</p>
